  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 9/7/2017 12:19 CT (17:19 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.5-PrintTemplates-newlabelcustomizationoptions\">Print Templates - new label customization options</h2><p>You now have the ability to customize the label for the &quot;Warranty Information&quot; and &quot;Notes&quot; sections on the ticket receipt and invoice templates!</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.5-VCTRe-AssignCashonHand\">VCT Re-Assign Cash on Hand</h2><p>The &quot;cash on hand&quot; field (starting cash) is not relevant when a VCT is re-assigned that is in a\u00a0de-assigned (not closed) state, so we have removed the field.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.5-ManagerCustomFormPermissions\">Manager Custom Form Permissions</h2><p>There were a few misconfigured\u00a0permissions for the manager role related to custom form field editing/deleting. These are now configured as intended.</p>",
